dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Milwaukee County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Milwaukee_Hydro_LINE_2021' and 'Milwaukee_Hydro_POLY_2021.' [Stream Lines in Milwaukee County, WI. Polygons representing open water in Milwaukee County, WI]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-mclio.opendata.arcgis.com/
